From 8f05e1c3b8f76695b3479ec6ccb29ebd3db66ee4 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Yonggang Luo <luoyonggang@gmail.com>
Date: Tue, 20 Jun 2023 22:37:00 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] add pthread_mutex_clocklock and pthread_cond_clockdwait

These two functions are already implemented in glibc, android bionic libc, qnx libc

Signed-off-by: Yonggang Luo <luoyonggang@gmail.com>
---
